### Driver cancels assigned ride (reason required)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rides/42/cancellations
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "cancelledBy": "DRIVER",
  "reason": "Passenger did not appear at pickup location",
  "scheduledStartTime": "2025-12-26T10:30:00"
}

